        <h1 class="animate-fade-up-1 text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl text-inst-navy leading-[1.1] mb-6" style="font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif; font-weight: 700;">
          Building the next generation of technology leaders.
        </h1>

        <p class="animate-fade-up-2 text-inst-gray text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
          The Griffith ICT Club is an inclusive community of students passionate about
          technology, spanning Nathan and Gold Coast campuses.
        </p>

        <div class="animate-fade-up-3 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="#community" class="bg-inst-navy hover:bg-inst-navy/90 text-white font-semibold px-7 py-3 rounded-lg transition-all duration-200 text-sm" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;">
